metadata.name: Relic
metadata.description: I was the best that could be offered, the epitome of all that men can dream of, I outshone all of my colleagues and was the ladiesâ€™ delight. But as time went on, I was left behind and people younger than me took my place; I became a RELIC. I am an object of historical interest, yes, I survive from an earlier age. I am a RELIC but I still have the interest of the modern.
